div.div:
Existing Data Platforms need to refine their
concepts to include Fabric as new capabilities
for integrated data processing, real time intelligence
and AI workloads.
At the same time there might be use cases which can
already start with Fabric and while they do not align with
all policies that are defined in parallel, they still develop
into the same direction.
Close alignment between the two is needed to prevent
common goal drift and diversion.
